episodes.title: CULT SURVIVOR! How I deprogrammed myself from 45 years of cult programming.How I got my freedom back
episodes.description:
Your journey to more success:
https://garycoxe.com/

Being part of a cult is challenging enough—but leaving one? That can be even harder.

In this video, I share my personal story of being born and raised in a cult, the extreme steps I had to take to protect my sanity, and how I fought to stay alive after leaving.

This was, without a doubt, the most difficult experience of my life—and I’ve been through my fair share of tragedy.

To my JW viewers who aren’t “supposed” to watch this (thanks to the programming that paints me as a villain, I'm so okay with it lol), I look forward to reading your comments.

For anyone trying to leave, considering it, or who has already left—know you’re not alone. If you need support, don’t hesitate to reach out, especially on Instagram.

Enjoy the video, and I’m excited to hear your thoughts in the comments. 💬
